choices.text: My brother and I caught up on old times. It was like no time had passed at all. We talked about how we were kids again. It was really cool to see how much we have all grown and changed. We talked about how we all have our own families now. We laughed and joked about how much we have all changed. I'm glad that we could all still be close even after all these years. I'm so grateful for that.
